      "raw_text": "Editor Press-The statement an\npearing in your issue of last night.\nin which Councilman Lambert is\nreported in favor of giving the\nmayor more power\" comes as II\nsurprise to members of the charter\nrevision committee who found Mr..\nLambert consistent opponent of\nthe amendment giving the mayor\ngreater powers.\n\n\nMr.. Lambert has submitted an\namendment which will go to the\npeople to be voted on, which in its\nnature does not begin to give the\nmayor as much power as the\namendmtnt proposed by the char\nter commission. The amendment\nproposed by Mr.. Lambert follows\nclosely the present city charter,"
